---
const healthUrl = "/api/health";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Webflow Builder Cloud</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        --bg: #071019;
        --bg2: #101f2e;
        --fg: #f4f6f8;
        --muted: #b7c5d3;
        --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        --accent: #7dd3fc;
        --accent2: #fbbf24;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.24), transparent 24%),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.18), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg2), var(--bg));
        color: var(--fg);
      }

      main {
        width: min(980px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 64px 0 72px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.22em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
        line-height: 0.96;
      }

      .lede {
        max-width: 58rem;
        margin: 20px 0 0;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-top: 36px;
      }

      @media (min-width: 840px) {
        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
        }
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 28px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        color: var(--accent2);
      }

      p,
      li {
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      code,
      a {
        color: var(--fg);
      }

      a.button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 12px 18px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: 1px solid rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.35);
        background: rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.12);
      }

      ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <p class="eyebrow">Webflow Cloud API</p>
      <h1>Repo Section Builder backend migration target.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        This Astro app is the new Webflow Cloud surface for the backend routes that previously ran
        on Netlify Functions. The existing Webflow Designer extension stays in the repo root and
        will be repointed here as the API migration completes.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Current state</h2>
          <p>
            The Cloud app scaffold is in place. The next migration step is replacing the current
            Postgres and Node-specific function runtime with Webflow Cloud-compatible API routes and
            SQLite-backed persistence.
          </p>
          <a class="button" href={healthUrl}>Check API health</a>
        </section>

        <aside class="card">
          <h2>Migration notes</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>The extension bundle remains separate and unchanged in the repo root.</li>
            <li>SQLite is the preferred Webflow Cloud storage target for this app.</li>
            <li>The existing Netlify handler contracts will be preserved where possible.</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
